With CPI coming in at 7.7% and SPX almost 4000, if not for FTX, I do think target would’ve hit.

-Tyranny of SBF

Probably a blessing in disguise for the Sol eco.

But in a few months, I'm guessing they're all going to be back to running the same predatory tokenomics. Capitalizing on our collective goldfish memory in this space.

Time is a flat circle.
